These Incredible Bob Dylan Quotes Are Life Changing

Robert Dylan is an American singer-songwriter, author and visual artist. Often regarded as one of the greatest songwriters of all time, Dylan has been a major figure in popular culture during a career spanning 60 years.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Bob Dylan. The best quotes and aphorisms of Bob Dylan that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Bob Dylan are definitely worth your time.
